sentences.sentence: The eluate can be used repeatedly or by other methods.
sentences.translation: 洗脱液可供多次或多种方法检测。

sentences.sentence: The proportions of flavin, non-heme iron and labile sulphide in the eluate was found to be 1: (8~10) :10.
sentences.translation: 经分析，其异咯嗪、非血红素铁以及不稳定硫之比为1：（8～10）：10。

sentences.sentence: On SDS-polyacrylamide gel electrophoresis (SDS-PAGE)the eluate from the column with the McAb coupled showed a single band, corresponding to the elution peak.
sentences.translation: 聚丙烯酰胺凝胶电泳显示单抗偶联柱层析洗脱物仅有单一区带与洗脱峰对应；
